      '`backend/src/modules/high-mobility/compatibility/hm-compatibility.types.ts` (neu): kanonische Types + Konstanten `PRESENT_COVERAGES`, `MISSING_COVERAGES`, `SUPPORTED_RATIO`, `NOT_RECOMMENDED_RATIO`.',
