      '`backend/src/modules/rental-health/rental-health.service.ts` (neu): `RentalHealthService.getVehicleHealth` fan-out `Promise.allSettled` Ãžber 7 Module-Outputs + `evaluateBattery`/`evaluateTires`/`evaluateBrakes`/`evaluateErrorCodes`/`evaluateServiceCompliance`/`evaluateComplaints`/`evaluateVehicleAlerts` + `computeOverallState` + `collectBlockingReasons`. `isRentalBlocked` = leaner Wrapper fÃžr den Booking-Gate (fail-open).',
      '`backend/src/modules/rental-health/rental-health.controller.ts` + `rental-health.module.ts` (neu): zwei GET-Routen (single + fleet, mit interner Batch-GrÃķÃe 20 um DB-Last zu kappen). `VehicleIntelligenceModule` + `HighMobilityModule` via `forwardRef` importiert. Modul in `backend/src/app.module.ts` registriert.',
      '`backend/src/modules/bookings/bookings.service.ts`: `RentalHealthService` per `@Inject(forwardRef(...))` injiziert; neuer Block in `create()` nach dem Overlap-Check â `ConflictException({ code: VEHICLE_RENTAL_BLOCKED, blockingReasons, vehicleId })`. `bookings.module.ts`: `RentalHealthModule` per `forwardRef` importiert.',
      '`frontend/src/lib/api.ts`: kanonische Types `RentalHealthState`/`RentalHealthModule`/`VehicleHealthResponse` + `api.rentalHealth.getVehicle`/`getFleet`. `frontend/src/rental/hooks/useVehicleHealth.ts` (neu): `useVehicleHealth` (single) + `useFleetHealthMap` (Map). `frontend/src/rental/components/rental-health/RentalHealthBadge.tsx` (neu): `RentalHealthBadge` + `RentalHealthModuleRow`.',
      '`frontend/src/rental/components/FleetView.tsx`: `useFleetHealthMap` fÃžr die gefilterten Vehicles; `RentalHealthBadge` ersetzt `HealthFleetIcon` in allen 4 Tabellen sobald Daten verfÃžgbar; âNicht vermietbar"-Pille neben Kennzeichen in Available/Reserved + Ready-Badge wird suppressed bei `rental_blocked=true`. `frontend/src/rental/components/NewBookingView.tsx`: `useFleetHealthMap` Ãžber volle Fleet-IDs (nicht gefilterte Subset, um Refetches zu vermeiden); Pille im Vehicle-Picker; Catch-Handler in `handleSaveBooking` erkennt `code=VEHICLE_RENTAL_BLOCKED` und rendert dedizierten Toast. `frontend/src/rental/components/BookingsView.tsx`: `useVehicleHealth` am Top-Level (nicht conditional) aus `detailVehicleId`; Warn-Banner + deaktivierter âPickup bestÃĪtigen"-Button im Detail-Sheet bei `rental_blocked=true`.',
