      'FIX C â ACCELERATION EVENT LOGIC: Entry threshold stays at 1.5 m/sÂē. Hysteresis continuation added at 1.2 m/sÂē to prevent fragmentation. Acceptance now requires sampleCount >= 2 AND deltaKmh >= 4.0 (removed sub-second duration filter, replaced with 1s-compatible sample-count logic). Rich metadata added: deltaKmh, sampleCount, mergedCount, startSpeedBand.',
