      'FIX E â FULL_BRAKING / POSSIBLE_IMPACT HARDENING: Both events now require a mini-window scanner (sampleCount >= 2), not a single pair. FULL_BRAKING: peakDecel >= 7.5 m/sÂē, startSpeed >= 20 km/h, deltaKmh >= 6.0. POSSIBLE_IMPACT: peakDecel >= 12.0 m/sÂē, startSpeed >= 25 km/h, deltaKmh >= 3.0. Single GPS spike artifacts can no longer trigger these critical events.',
      'FIX F â LAUNCH_LIKE_START REFINEMENT: LAUNCH_CONTROL renamed to LAUNCH_LIKE_START. startSpeed requirement tightened to <= 3 km/h (was < 8 km/h). peakAccel >= 3.5 m/sÂē now required in the acceleration window. Events above 3 km/h start speed are classified as aggressive acceleration only, not launch-like.',
